Definition: reflect light or colors like an opal
Example: Distant clouds opalesce like pale brocade; raindrops caught in a sunbeam seem to opalesce
Synonyms: adj, all, bright, opalescent, noun, attribute, opalescence, reflect, light, or, colors, like, an, opal, Distant, clouds, pale, brocade, raindrops, caught, in, a, sunbeam, seem, to
Frame: 1
Category: verb.weather
